中 什么扮演了 拉格朗日乘子 的角色？
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

拉氏量为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\mathcal{L} & =\frac{-1}{4}F_{\mu\nu}F^{\mu\nu}+\frac{1}{2}m^{2}A_{\mu}A^{\mu}-A_{\mu}J^{\mu}\\
 & =\frac{1}{2}A_{\nu}\left[g^{\mu\nu}\left(\square+m^{2}\right)-\partial^{\mu}\partial^{\nu}\right]A^{\mu}-A_{\mu}J^{\mu}\\
 & =\frac{1}{2}A_{\mu}\left(\square+m^{2}\right)A^{\mu}{\color{blue}-A_{\mu}\partial^{\mu}\left(\partial\cdot A\right)}-A_{\mu}J^{\mu}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

运动学方程为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\square+m^{2}\right)A^{\mu}=J^{\mu},\quad\partial\cdot A=0
\]

\end_inset

代入 
\begin_inset Formula $\partial\cdot A=0$
\end_inset

 的约束得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathcal{L}=\frac{1}{2}A_{\mu}\left(\square+m^{2}\right)A^{\mu}-A_{\mu}J^{\mu}
\]

\end_inset

再求运动方程得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\square+m^{2}\right)A^{\mu}=J^{\mu}
\]

\end_inset

不能得到之前的约束。所以 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{\mu}\partial^{\mu}\left(\partial\cdot A\right)$
\end_inset

就是拉格朗日乘子？？
